{
  "id": "adv_card_mhk_03_03",
  "title": "miho 3話  見ていてくれるはず",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん\n……今は、麻奈のことをどう思ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho-san‚\n…How do you feel about Mana now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "嫌いですよ。先日もそう申し上げたと思いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I dislike her. I believe I mentioned it before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0333333651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、琴乃達の歌がまだ下手だというなら\nいちいちアドバイスをする意味はないと思いますけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that's the case‚ and you still think Kotono and the others sing poorly‚\nthen there's no point in giving advice each time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0999996502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈の歌が、あんなつまらないものと思われたら\n記録を塗り替えてやる甲斐がなくなるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Nagase Mana's singing is perceived as that uninteresting‚\nThere's no point in striving to surpass her record‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666663169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "塗り替える……ですか\n以前は、抹殺するとおっしゃっていましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To surpass it…?\nPreviously‚ you said you wanted to erase her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0333324749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう考えるのは、もうやめました\n……きっと、葉ちゃんはそれを望んでいないと思うので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've stopped thinking that way.\n…I'm sure‚ You wouldn't want that anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2999981243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "私達の実力で、今度こそあの人を上回ってみせます\n誰にも、長瀬麻奈を思い出す隙なんて与えないくらい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With our abilities‚ this time‚ we'll definitely surpass her.\nSo much so that nobody will even have a chance to remember Mana Nagase.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.7999981243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈を負かしたいというのは、変わらないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You still want to defeat Mana‚ don't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5333337465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、逆恨みなのは分かってますよ\nでも、それの何が悪いって言うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I know it's resentment.\nBut what's wrong with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8000004131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "たとえマネージャーでも\n個人的な動機にまで口を出されるいわれはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even as a manager‚\nthere's no reason to intervene in personal motives.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6666642824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITYでの出来事は、姫野さんの仕業で\nmihoさんがやった訳じゃないと知ってはいますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The incident at I-UNITY was Himeno-san's doing‚\nI know it wasn't you‚ miho-san‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8999960898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "振り回されたトリエルと瑠依は本当に気の毒でしたよ\nなんで止めてくれなかったのかと、今でも思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE and Rui were really pitiable for being manipulated like that.\nI still wonder why you didn't stop it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1333299318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……でしょうね\nそれは……本当に申し訳なく思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ I understand.\nI'm… truly sorry for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3666597047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それに麻奈の曲は、俺達にはとても大事なもので――\nそれを消し去ろうとしたのは、絶対に許せません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moreover‚ Mana's songs are very important to us――\nTrying to erase it is absolutely unforgivable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0666597047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、貴方や他の子達を酷く傷つけたと思います\n……本当に、ごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ I think I really hurt you and the other girls.\n…I'm really sorry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5666530922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……誰かを恨まないとやってられない気持ちは\n今なら、俺も少しは分かるつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… the feeling of not being able to go on without hating someone‚\nI think I understand it a bit now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ですから俺も、mihoさんが正々堂々と振る舞う限り\nもう、あの時の話は蒸し返さないことにします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So as long as miho-san behaves honorably‚\nI won't bring up that time again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7333207761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……正々堂々と、しなかったら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If I don't behave honorably?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.866650549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "その時は……まぁ、少なくとも\nスリクスのマネージャーは降りるでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then… well‚ at the very least‚\nIIIX's manager will quit the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1999899858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "はっきり言えばいいでしょう\nその時こそ、どんな手を使ってでも必ずぶっ潰すって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should just say it plainly.\nThen‚ at that time‚ I'll definitely crush them by any means necessary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2000052446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ぶっ潰すって……\nkanaさんの口癖が少し移ってませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Crush them…\nAre you picking up kana-san's catchphrase a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4333385779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "嫌なこと言わないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't say weird things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9000164343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……でも本当に、祭典を欠席して良かったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But really‚ was it okay to miss the festival?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.5000143998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "Sundanceと葉さんを忘れてほしくないなら\nなおさら、祭典には出た方が良かったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't want people to forget Sundance and You-san‚\nthen shouldn't you have gone to the festival even more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.0000143998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.8000215206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.7166668248
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.7166668248
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.9666668248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です\nさっきテスト撮影が終わって、そろそろ本番だそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work.\nThe test shoot just ended‚ and the actual shoot is about to start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6333334915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.4666658076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "さっきそこで見てました、凄い迫力でしたね\nこれならMVもかなりいいものが出来そうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw it earlier; it was really powerful.\nWith this‚ the MV is likely to turn out quite well too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.0333324742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.1333324742
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "ライブでのお披露目も評判良かったですから\n完成版はあれよりもっといいものにしないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live was well received too‚\nwe need to make the final version even better than that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.1333324742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.0999991409
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
