      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、本番の撮影が始まるみたいです\nそれでは、行って来ますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ it looks like the main shoot is starting.\nWell then‚ I'll be off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.6333324742,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
