      "text": "（あの時、mihoさんはこう言ってた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（At that time‚ miho-san said this.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.1666769973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "Sundanceと葉さんを忘れてほしくないなら\nなおさら、祭典には出た方が良かったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't want people to forget Sundance and You-san‚\nthen shouldn't you have gone to the festival even more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.3333416294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "それは……葉ちゃんは、ファンの人達に\n喜んでもらいたいといつも言っていましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… You always used to say\nshe wanted to make the fans happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.6000052443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "それなら私はスリクスとして、ファンに届ける\n新曲に取り組んだ方がいいと思っただけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ as a member of IIIX‚ I thought it would be best to\nwork on a new song to deliver to the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.8666617384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_03_03-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "……葉ちゃんに笑われないように、私も頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I have to work hard so I won't be laughed at by You.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.0666576693,
      "sfxList": [
